WEBVTT

00:05:27.184 --> 00:05:31.183
create a toxic cocktail of pride,

00:05:31.207 --> 00:05:34.001
arrogance, paranoia,

00:05:34.025 --> 00:05:36.467
that drug them both to war.

00:05:38.177 --> 00:05:40.080
Which brings me to the big idea:

00:05:41.090 --> 00:05:42.558
Thucydides's Trap.

00:05:43.701 --> 00:05:46.982
"Thucydides's Trap" is a term
I coined several years ago,

00:05:47.006 --> 00:05:49.593
to make vivid Thucydides's insight.

00:05:50.569 --> 00:05:54.799
Thucydides's Trap is the dangerous
dynamic that occurs

00:05:54.823 --> 00:05:58.656
when a rising power threatens
to displace a ruling power,

00:05:58.680 --> 00:06:00.404
like Athens --